c: 2
v: 167
t: "Abbobti kataatak Suge mari Diggah Addunyâ fanah gacim luk Suginninoy, Toysa nanu Bari keenik Akkuk nen usun nek Bari kah yekken innah iyyan, Yalli Qhiyaamah Ayro gibdi digaala ken kah yuybullee innah ken uma taamoomiy Abak Sugeeni ken yaybulleh Nadaama keenil takkem keh, usun girak inki innah yawqe mara hinnon"